  [Excerpt] Berlin (DPA) -- The Bundeswehr continues to 
wonder what happened to about 81,000 tonnes of Russian 
ammunition in eastern Germany. This was confirmed by the German 
liaison command with the Western Group of Russian Forces in 
Berlin on Wednesday [16 February]. In view of the high risk, 
