<H3> <TI>   * Pasqua Role in Iraqi Official's Visit </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  94P20343A Paris LE POINT in French 29 Jan 94 p 17--FOR 
OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> 94P20343A </F>
<F P=104>  Paris LE POINT </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> French </F>
Article Type:CSO 

  [Text] Interior Minister Charles Pasqua played a 
determining role in the Paris visit of Tariq `Aziz last October. 
Iraq's number two man, officially in Paris to seek medical 
attention, had numerous political and economic conversations. At 
an emergency meeting of the appropriate ministers, it had been 
decided that no contact would take place. The decision came too 
late: Pasqua had already met with `Aziz the previous day. 

</TEXT>

