<H3> <TI>   Ministries Say No Troop Reinforcements Planned for Bosnia </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD1602165594 Brussels La Une Radio Network in French 1600 
GMT 16 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1602165594 </F>
<F P=104>  Brussels La Une Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> French </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpt] [passage omitted] According to the Belgian 
Ministries of Foreign Affairs and Defense, there are no plans to 
send reinforcements to Bosnia. Moreover, the United Nations has 
not made any request to this effect, nor is there any question 
of moving to Bosnia a certain number of the peacekeeping troops 
currently being deployed in the Baranya region. Furthermore, 
France, the Netherlands, and Great Britain are all refusing to 
send additional troops to Bosnia. 

</TEXT>

