<H3> <TI>   Government Denies Entry Visa for Zhirinovskiy </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD1602194694 Madrid RNE-1 Radio Network in Spanish 1900 GMT 
16 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1602194694 </F>
<F P=104>  Madrid RNE-1 Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Spanish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The Spanish Government has prohibited the entry into 
our country of Vladimir Zhirinovskiy, the ultranationalist 
leader and winner of the last Russian legislative elections, who 
was going to take part in a television program. 
  According to sources at the Diplomatic Information Office, 
he 
has been refused an entry visa because his presence in Spain is 
not considered appropriate, a measure which had already been 
adopted by other European countries. 

</TEXT>

