<DOCNO> FBIS3-39549 </DOCNO>
<HT>    "drweu034aa_94003" </HT>


<HEADER>
<AU>   FBIS-WEU-94-034 </AU>
Document Type:Daily Report 
<DATE1>  18 February 1994 </DATE1>

