  The FDP politician called on the CDU to make a clear 
commitment to Europe at its party congress. There are some 
forces in the CDU that want to reinterpret Europe and want 
Germany to follow a special path. Kinkel said anyone who wants 
to reduce Germany's share in the process of European unification 
is cutting off the branch on which he is sitting. 

