<H4>   Italy Says News `Encouraging' </H4>
<F P=102> LD2002150494 Rome RAI Televideo Teletext in Italian 1437 GMT 
20 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2002150494 </F>
<F P=104>  Rome RAI Televideo Teletext </F>


