Language: <F P=105> Italian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] [Italian] Defense Minister Fabio Fabbri said at a 
summit of five NATO defense ministers held in Aviano that "the 
decision of the international community to bring the Yugoslav 
crisis under control is now irreversible." 
  As for the ultimatum, Fabbri said that "a full enforcement 
of 
the conditions set by the NATO order is required. There can be 
no bargains and no gifts. However, the news we received during 
our discussions is encouraging." 

